No. 575. Hong Wing, Petitioner, v. The United States; Wong Ding Chong, Petitioner, v. The United States; Dang Ming, Petitioner, v. The United States; Wong Wah, Petitioner, v. The United States; and Lam Loy, Petitioner, v. The United States. No. 576. No. 577. No. 578. No. 579. March 5, 1906. Mr. Francis J. Wing for petitioners. The Attorney General and The Solicitor General for respondent.

Petitions for writs of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the' Sixth Circuit denied.
